name: Unidentified_Jawa_warlord
content:
A Jawa warlord operated on an astronomical object with canyons and bat-like creatures. At one point during the Galactic Civil War between the Galactic Empire and the Alliance to Restore the Republic, the warlord was present in the vicinity of a sandcrawler and proclaimed "This is mine, all mine!" in Jawaese. The Jawa had yellow eyes, wore brown robes and bandoliers attributed to the species, and used an ion blaster.
The character was depicted on the "Jawa Warlord" card for The Price of Victory, an expansion set of cards for the Star Wars Galaxies Trading Card Game. The Jawa was illustrated by artist Kerem Beyit.
